text:
If you're serious about learning SEO the best way is to use a premium course. I can highly recommend the SEO Blueprint. You'll get really good at technical SEO, learn some exclusive link building techniques and you'll get tons of more value from the private FB community. <https://seoblueprint.com/|https://seoblueprint.com/>

If you're looking for an alternative you can go with Ryan Stewart course. It's a lot more expensive since it's targeted towards agencies. But it has some additional nuggets that could be helpful. <https://theblueprint.training/|https://theblueprint.training/>
